 * 
 * Pin Configuration:
 * - Pin 26: Motor Forward
 * - Pin 27: Motor Backward  
 * - Pin 25: Motor Left
 * - Pin 33: Motor Right
 * - Pin 32: PWM Speed Control
 * - Pin 34: Temperature Sensor
 * - Pin 35: Battery Monitor
 * - Pin 2:  Status LED
 * - Pin 4:  Error LED
 * - Pin 5:  Buzzer
